---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Anchita Hari - Software Engineer">
  	<main class="bento-main">
    	<div class="bento-grid">

		<!-- Hero card -->
		<div class="bento-card hero-card fade-in">
			<div class="hero-top">
			<img src="/anchita.png" alt="Anchita Hari" class="avatar" />
			</div>
			<h1 class="bento-name">Anchita <em>Hari</em><br>Narayanan</h1>
			<div class="role-pills">
			<span class="pill">Software Engineer</span>
			<span class="pill">Go + AWS</span>
			<span class="pill">Learning in public</span>
			</div>
			<p class="bento-bio">Engineer by day. Learner by night. Currently figuring out what kind of engineer I want to become next.</p>
			<div class="bento-actions">
			<button class="btn-primary" onclick="window.toggleChat()">Ask me anything</button>
			<a href="/resume.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn-ghost">Resume</a>
			<a href="https://github.com/your-username/anchita-dev" target="_blank" class="btn-ghost">GitHub</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Building in public card -->
		<div class="bento-card building-card fade-in">
			<div class="card-label">
			<span class="signal-dot"></span>
			IN PROGRESS
			</div>
			<h2 class="card-heading">What I'm building</h2>
			<p class="card-text">Currently rebuilding my personal site from scratch with a Go backend, Kubernetes, and an AI chatbot powered by RAG while documenting all my progress in public!</p>
			<div class="phase-pills">
			<span class="phase-pill done">Go server</span>
			<span class="phase-pill done">Docker + EKS</span>
			<span class="phase-pill done">Astro frontend</span>
			<span class="phase-pill done">RAG chatbot</span>
			<span class="phase-pill done">CI/CD</span>
			</div>
			<a href="/projects" class="card-link">View all projects →</a>
		</div>

		<!-- Latest post card -->
		<div class="bento-card post-card fade-in">
			<div class="card-label">LATEST POST</div>
			<h2 class="card-heading">Growth doesn't happen on its own</h2>
			<p class="card-text">Recently, I've been sitting with an uncomfortable truth. Growth doesn't happen on its own, you have to go looking for it.</p>
			<a href="/writing" class="card-link">View all posts →</a>
		</div>

		<!-- About card -->
		<div class="bento-card about-card fade-in" id="about">
			<div class="about-card-inner">
				<div class="about-card-left">
					<p class="card-label">ABOUT</p>
					<h2 class="section-heading">The story so far</h2>
				</div>
			<div class="about-card-right">
				<p>
					I'm a software engineer based in <strong>McLean, VA</strong>, currently working at Capital One
					in Card Tech, specifically in Card Acquisitions. I contribute to backend systems in <strong>Go and Java</strong>
					and work extensively with <strong>AWS</strong>.
				</p>
				<p>
					After almost four years of engineering, I've realized that the work I find most energizing isn't
					just shipping features. It's the moments where I get to <strong>teach, explain, and help others grow</strong>
					whether that's mentoring teammates, documenting systems clearly, or translating technical decisions
					into plain language.
				</p>
				<p>
					This site is a project I'm building in public to keep that energy going outside of work. I am
					<strong>deepening my expertise in Go, learning Kubernetes and AI integration</strong>, and
					documenting everything along the way so someone else doesn't have to figure it out alone.
				</p>
				<p>
					Outside of work, I'm a Virginia Tech CS alum who has always been drawn to mentoring and teaching
					and actively sought those opportunities. My favorite piece of advice to give is that
					<strong>discomfort is a sign you're heading in the right direction</strong>. I'm still learning
					to follow it myself.
				</p>
			</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Connect card -->
		<div class="bento-card connect-card fade-in">
			<div class="card-label">CONNECT</div>
			<h2 class="card-heading">Whether you are figuring your path out in tech or have wisdom to share, I'd love to connect </h2>
			<div class="connect-links">
				<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/anchita-hn" target="_blank" class="connect-item">
					<span class="connect-icon">in</span>
					<span>LinkedIn</span>
				</a>
				<a href="https://github.com/anchitahari" target="_blank" class="connect-item">
					<span class="connect-icon">gh</span>
					<span>GitHub</span>
				</a>
				<a href="mailto:anchita.hari@gmail.com" class="connect-item">
					<span class="connect-icon">@</span>
					<span>Email</span>
				</a>
			</div>
			</div>
		</div>
  	</main>
</Layout>